{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"10":"The Chapters on Divorce"},"section_detail":{"10":{"hadithnumber_first":2016,"hadithnumber_last":2477,"arabicnumber_first":2016,"arabicnumber_last":2477}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2464,"arabicnumber":2464,"text":"Rapporté par Tawus que Ibn 'Abbas a dit que le Messager d’Allah (ﷺ) a simplement dit : “Pour l’un de vous, donner (sa terre) à son frère est mieux pour lui que de recevoir un loyer fixe pour elle.”","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Agreed Upon"}],"reference":{"book":10,"hadith":49}}]}